{"tid":1589751,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［小常識］你應該慶幸你用緊嘅透明膠電話殼會變黃，因為咁先反而較安全","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:38:43.000Z","uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88cabf17d02e1e9893a6a28104fe8092f8e9d73f","tid":1589751,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:00:11.000Z","msg":"蘋果、小米等大品牌的5款手機殼，不但被驗出含有毒有害物質，如有多環芬烴、塑化劑、鉛、短鏈氯化石蠟等，且含量均超出標準<br />\n<br />\n透明材質的手機殼容易發黃變色，但相對會較安全。最危險的是閃粉水鑽類的手機殼，「愈漂亮的手機殼可能愈有毒！」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出新機成日見到啲人嫌棄透明殼易黄，黄咗就換個新嘅啦<br />\n唔通用一世咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17253af10d462726990b8a4d033fbb6b18a8add","tid":1589751,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"d2511c45ac02045570e3f7f2123b23c95b215570","tid":1589751,"uid":149959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"Source?"}]}